omments":0,"created_at":"2022-01-09T01:57:35Z","updated_at":"2022-01-09T22:02:55Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/43724","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/43724","diff_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/43724.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/43724.patch","merged_at":null},"body":"This replaces `reshape` with `ReshapedArray` in the definition of `kron`. They should never escape. The reason to do so is to save a few allocations:
